        {
            "title": "霍爾木茲海峽船舶追蹤：伊朗向部分商船收取「過路費」",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 仍有少量船隻繼續通過<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"霍爾木茲海峽\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:霍爾木茲海峽;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/霍爾木茲海峽\">霍爾木茲海峽</a>，德黑蘭對每航次收取最高200萬美元費用，實際上相當於在這條關鍵水道設立了非正式的「過路費」機制。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">周一共有五艘船似乎駛離<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"波斯灣\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:波斯灣;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/波斯灣\">波斯灣</a>，另有三艘駛入波斯灣。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">不過，伊朗伊斯蘭革命衛隊海軍迫使貨櫃船Selen掉頭。該船上周進入波斯灣後，周二試圖駛離該海灣。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/yetNO7LnipqkkQpDp0BgTA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/67fd20a404e3bbe6bac64d9c3bca3632\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">幾乎所有被觀測到的船隻通行路線都貼近拉熱克島和霍爾木茲海峽之間的一條狹窄航道，該航道處於伊朗近海深處。航運路線的這一變化顯示，德黑蘭正通過戰術性調整，試圖加強對這一關鍵能源通道的控制。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-50a9c016-716b-3ea4-9e66-941fab17b946-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">電子干擾持續擾亂該地區的船舶追蹤系統。此外，船舶在高風險水域關閉自動識別系統(AIS)應答器，進一步降低了跟蹤數據的及時性和可靠性。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/15WB_T0Oix2pwx9Rb2n1mw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/0029426853552c2488c21d291988ea6a\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博匯編的船舶追蹤數據顯示，周一清晨，兩艘印度液化石油氣(LPG)運輸船和一艘伊朗超級油輪被觀測到駛離波斯灣。隨後又有一艘成品油油輪和一艘散貨船跟著離開。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">一艘此前被列為報廢的船隻周日也被發現在霍爾木茲海峽，這是近期第二艘所謂「殭屍船」通過這條關鍵水道。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由於船舶在高風險水域關閉航行信息，通行船舶數量最初可能看似較少，但隨著延遲數據的陸續發布，該數據可能會被上調。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">周一，散貨船Ardavan和貨櫃船Jasmin這兩艘與伊朗有關的船隻駛入波斯灣。周二，一艘中國所有的化學品/成品油運輸船也完成通行。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/5ZEAf5Qvbuw_PWbj2whnfQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/0c6d4d724d52fd052fef69f40ff38bf4\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">注：</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由於船舶在遠離霍爾木茲海峽之前可能不會發送位置信息，為識別可能駛離或進入波斯灣的船隻，覆蓋阿曼灣、阿拉伯海和紅海等更大範圍的自動定位系統信號被匯總</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">當發現潛在通行船舶後，會進一步研究信號記錄，以判斷相關航行是否真實，還是由信號欺騙所致，電子干擾可能會偽造船舶的實際位置</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">如果船舶的應答器尚未重新開啟，一些航行活動可能無法被探測到。與伊朗有關的油輪從波斯灣駛出經常不發送信號，直到約10天後經阿聯酋富查伊拉抵達馬六甲海峽。其他船舶可能也採取了類似策略，因此可能數日內都不會出現在追蹤屏幕上</p></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題HORMUZ TRACKER: Iran Charges Ships to Transit Vital Chokepoint</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"1\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
